        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/al_osterheld/{size}/611_2.png",
        "created_at": "2020-08-02T21:22:16.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yes, they planted an acre of Pinot Noir from seeds, I think next to the Memorius vineyard rather than part of it. It\u2019s a long term project where they will select and eventually propagate some of the material. I don\u2019t think they have sold wine from those vines, though.</p>\n<p>There was a longer story written up about the project, don\u2019t recall whether it was here or somewhere else.</p>\n<p>-Al</p>",
